Package: stb-tester
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, curl, gstreamer0.10-plugins-bad, gstreamer0.10-plugins-base, gstreamer0.10-plugins-good, gstreamer0.10-tools, gstreamer0.10-x, moreutils, openssh-client, pylint, python (>= 2.7), python-flask, python-gst0.10, python-gtk2, python-jinja2, python-opencv, tesseract-ocr
Description: Automated User Interface testing for set-top boxes. 
 stb-tester tests a set-top-box by issuing commands to it using a remote-control
 and checking that it has done the right thing by analysing what is on screen.
 Test scripts are written in Python and can be generated with the `stbt record`
 command.
